'''Michael P. Kube-McDowell''' (or K-Mac, as he calls himself) is a science-fiction author. He has published thirteen novels, including the three books of [[The Black Fleet Crisis]] trilogy.

"Michael P. Kube-McDowell" is a pen name. The author's real name is simply Michael Paul McDowell. The "Kube" part of his pen name is pronounced "CUE-bee."<ref name="Before the Storm">''[[Before the Storm]]''</ref>

